# Window & Application Management

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+N` | New Window | Create new Ghostty window |
| `Cmd+Q` | Quit | Quit Ghostty application |
| `Cmd+Shift+W` | Close Window | Close current window |
| `Cmd+W` | Close Surface | Close current surface |
| `Cmd+Shift+,` | Reload Config | Reload configuration file |
| `Cmd+,` | Open Config | Open configuration file in editor |
| `Cmd+Shift+P` | Command Palette | Toggle command palette |
| `Cmd+Option+I` | Inspector | Toggle developer inspector |

# Tab Management

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+T` | New Tab | Create new tab |
| `Cmd+Option+W` | Close Tab | Close current tab |
| `Cmd+1` - `Cmd+8` | Go to Tab 1-8 | Jump to specific tab |
| `Cmd+9` | Last Tab | Jump to last tab |
| `Ctrl+Tab` | Next Tab | Switch to next tab |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Tab` | Previous Tab | Switch to previous tab |
| `Cmd+Shift+[` | Previous Tab | Switch to previous tab |
| `Cmd+Shift+]` | Next Tab | Switch to next tab |

# Split Pane Management

## Creating Splits

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+D` | New Split Right | Create vertical split (right) |
| `Cmd+Shift+D` | New Split Down | Create horizontal split (down) |

## Navigating Splits

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+Option+↑` | Go to Split Above | Move focus to split above |
| `Cmd+Option+↓` | Go to Split Below | Move focus to split below |
| `Cmd+Option+←` | Go to Split Left | Move focus to split left |
| `Cmd+Option+→` | Go to Split Right | Move focus to split right |
| `Cmd+[` | Previous Split | Go to previous split |
| `Cmd+]` | Next Split | Go to next split |

## Resizing Splits

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+Ctrl+↑` | Resize Split Up | Resize split upward by 10 |
| `Cmd+Ctrl+↓` | Resize Split Down | Resize split downward by 10 |
| `Cmd+Ctrl+←` | Resize Split Left | Resize split leftward by 10 |
| `Cmd+Ctrl+→` | Resize Split Right | Resize split rightward by 10 |
| `Cmd+Ctrl+=` | Equalize Splits | Make all splits equal size |

## Split Display

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+Shift+Enter` | Toggle Split Zoom | Zoom current split to fullscreen |
| `Cmd+Enter` | Toggle Fullscreen | Toggle fullscreen mode |
| `Cmd+Ctrl+F` | Toggle Fullscreen | Toggle fullscreen mode |

# Text Selection & Clipboard

## Selection

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+A` | Select All | Select all text in buffer |
| `Shift+↑` | Adjust Selection Up | Extend selection upward |
| `Shift+↓` | Adjust Selection Down | Extend selection downward |
| `Shift+←` | Adjust Selection Left | Extend selection left |
| `Shift+→` | Adjust Selection Right | Extend selection right |
| `Shift+Home` | Adjust Selection Home | Extend selection to line start |
| `Shift+End` | Adjust Selection End | Extend selection to line end |
| `Shift+Page Up` | Adjust Selection Page Up | Extend selection one page up |
| `Shift+Page Down` | Adjust Selection Page Down | Extend selection one page down |

## Copy & Paste

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+C` | Copy | Copy selection to clipboard |
| `Cmd+V` | Paste | Paste from clipboard |
| `Cmd+Shift+V` | Paste Selection | Paste from selection buffer |

# Scrolling & Navigation

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+Home` | Scroll to Top | Jump to top of scrollback |
| `Cmd+End` | Scroll to Bottom | Jump to bottom of scrollback |
| `Cmd+Page Up` | Scroll Page Up | Scroll up one page |
| `Cmd+Page Down` | Scroll Page Down | Scroll down one page |
| `Cmd+↑` | Jump to Previous Prompt | Jump to previous shell prompt |
| `Cmd+↓` | Jump to Next Prompt | Jump to next shell prompt |
| `Cmd+Shift+↑` | Jump to Previous Prompt | Jump to previous shell prompt |
| `Cmd+Shift+↓` | Jump to Next Prompt | Jump to next shell prompt |

# Font & Display

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd++` | Increase Font Size | Increase font size by 1 |
| `Cmd+=` | Increase Font Size | Increase font size by 1 |
| `Cmd+-` | Decrease Font Size | Decrease font size by 1 |
| `Cmd+0` | Reset Font Size | Reset font to default size |

# Screen & Output Management

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+K` | Clear Screen | Clear screen (keeps scrollback) |
| `Cmd+Option+Shift+J` | Write Screen to File (Open) | Save screen contents and open |
| `Cmd+Ctrl+Shift+J` | Write Screen to File (Copy) | Save screen contents and copy path |
| `Cmd+Shift+J` | Write Screen to File (Paste) | Save screen contents and paste path |

# Text Input & Editing

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Shift+Enter` | Newline with Escape | Send escape + newline (`\x1b\r`) |
| `Cmd+←` | Beginning of Line | Move cursor to line start (`\x01`) |
| `Cmd+→` | End of Line | Move cursor to line end (`\x05`) |
| `Cmd+Backspace` | Delete Line | Delete from cursor to line start (`\x15`) |
| `Option+←` | Word Left | Move cursor one word left |
| `Option+→` | Word Right | Move cursor one word right |

# Undo & Redo

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+Z` | Undo | Undo last action |
| `Cmd+Shift+Z` | Redo | Redo last undone action |
| `Cmd+Shift+T` | Undo | Undo last action |

# Window Management

| Shortcut | Action | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `Cmd+Option+Shift+W` | Close All Windows | Close all Ghostty windows |
| `Cmd+Shift+I` | Change Title | Prompt to change window/tab title |

# Special Keys

Some keybindings send special terminal control sequences or clipboard operations that don't have visible shortcuts in menus.

---

## Notes

- **Cmd** = Command key (⌘)
- **Option** = Alt/Option key (⌥)
- **Ctrl** = Control key (⌃)
- **Shift** = Shift key (⇧)
- **super** in config = Cmd key on macOS
- **alt** in config = Option key on macOS

## Custom Keybindings

The following keybindings are custom additions to the default configuration:

- `Cmd+Shift+I` → Change Title (added 2025-10-08)

## Configuration File

Current configuration: `/Users/terryli/.config/ghostty/config`

